	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "NOT caused by this cleanup — test_linting_error_detection fails independently of every change here (survived reqwest removal AND cargo update). the empty-context-tag diagnostic range end_col shifted 37 -> 34, i.e. the committed snapshot is stale against the current tree-sitter-actions grammar pin (same submodule-drift theme as the CI break). decide whether 34 is correct (accept snapshot) or a grammar regression before running cargo insta accept" ;
