<urn:uuid:fbeed33b-787a-5702-aa16-37fd42a87478> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051> <urn:uuid:019db111-0014-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0013-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0012-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0011-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0010-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0009-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0008-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0007-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0006-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0005-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0004-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0003-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0002-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0001-7000-0000-000000000001> .
<urn:uuid:344f2a0d-1a93-537a-b42b-a0cd1b6c7760> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasSubCharter> <urn:uuid:fbeed33b-787a-5702-aa16-37fd42a87478> .
<urn:uuid:fbeed33b-787a-5702-aa16-37fd42a87478> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCharterState> "Closed" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasAlias> "parse_boundary" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The parser currently has two behaviors (strict failure and recoverable parse), but command-level handling is inconsistent. This creates unsafe edges where partial recovery can silently become destructive file rewrites.\n\nThis charter defines a single parse boundary contract for the platform: syntax errors are systemic and block mutation; lint remains advisory for valid parses. It also defines observability hooks so parse health is measurable over time rather than inferred from incidents." ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "fbeed33b-787a-5702-aa16-37fd42a87478" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Parse Boundary and Mutation Safety" ;
	a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Charter> .
<urn:uuid:8e798316-ed1f-512c-91d3-d02eceb47c48> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Charter> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Observability and Debugging Tools" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "8e798316-ed1f-512c-91d3-d02eceb47c48" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Right now debugging the clearhead system requires `RUST_LOG=debug` and reading source code — you can't inspect what the graph actually contains, why a SPARQL query returned nothing, or what the system resolved a charter name to.\n\nThe architecture already has everything needed to fix this: the RDF store is queryable, the domain model is structured, and the CLI is the right place to expose it. The goal is to make the system self-describing so that bugs like the \"recursive charter returns empty\" class can be diagnosed in seconds, not hours.\n\nLonger term, this is also the foundation for unifying telemetry — if events are written as RDF triples into the store, `query sparql` becomes the single interface for debugging, analytics, and introspection." ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasAlias> "observability" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCharterState> "Closed" .
<urn:uuid:344f2a0d-1a93-537a-b42b-a0cd1b6c7760> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasSubCharter> <urn:uuid:8e798316-ed1f-512c-91d3-d02eceb47c48> .
<urn:uuid:8e798316-ed1f-512c-91d3-d02eceb47c48> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051> <urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1b8-7e63-a96f-10d0816b25ac> , <urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1be-7ea3-a056-51ae79a826d9> , <urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1c5-79c3-9c4a-952ad4514ccc> , <urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1ce-7842-bbf6-27f3b36feef4> .
<urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1b8-7e63-a96f-10d0816b25ac> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019cffdc-b1b8-7e63-a96f-10d0816b25ac" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "add sparql query command to CLI" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "clearhead query sparql '<query>' runs the query against the live workspace RDF graph and returns results. the graph infrastructure already exists — this is mostly wiring run_workspace_sql_query to a new subcommand. would have cut the recursive-charter debug session from hours to minutes" ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-03-18T16:17:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1be-7ea3-a056-51ae79a826d9> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019cffdc-b1be-7ea3-a056-51ae79a826d9" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "add graph inspection command" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "clearhead show graph [--charter X] dumps the actual RDF triples for a charter or the whole workspace. critical for verifying hasSubCharter triples exist and point to the right URIs — was completely blind on this during the recursive charter fix" ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-03-18T16:23:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1c5-79c3-9c4a-952ad4514ccc> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019cffdc-b1c5-79c3-9c4a-952ad4514ccc" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "improve empty result messages for charter queries" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "when --charter X returns zero plans, tell the user what was actually resolved and why nothing matched: e.g. 'resolved charter to Build the ClearHead Platform (explicit, README.md), graph name: build_clearhead, SPARQL returned 0 results'. silent empty with exit 0 is the worst failure mode for a query system" ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-03-18T16:23:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1ce-7842-bbf6-27f3b36feef4> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019cffdc-b1ce-7842-bbf6-27f3b36feef4" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "unify telemetry with RDF store" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "current try_emit/TelemetryEvent is outward-facing product analytics. if events were written as RDF triples into the oxigraph store, query sparql would serve debugging, analytics, and introspection from one interface. worth exploring after the query command exists so we can see what it would look like" ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-05-17T16:34:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
