<urn:uuid:019f268f-eb47-7f57-b8c7-2ba766b74e7a> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019f268f-eb47-7f57-b8c7-2ba766b74e7a" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "drop the vestigial opts parameter from the parse wrapper chain" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "get_action_list_struct threads an unused serde_json Value through tests and archive.rs — a leftover from the js-style options era. done: dropped the opts param entirely (signature is now get_action_list_struct(actions: &str)), updated the one production call site (archive.rs) and all test/example call sites (tests/lib.rs x11, tests/error_reporting.rs, tests/snapshots_from_examples.rs, examples/format_demo.rs). also deleted get_action_list — the JSON-Value-returning wrapper around it — which turned out to have zero callers anywhere, production or test" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#requiresContext> <urn:context:cli> ;
