<urn:uuid:019f268f-eb48-7c81-ad4c-748ece362373> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019f268f-eb48-7c81-ad4c-748ece362373" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "extract build_workspace_store from the query helpers" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "run_workspace_raw_query and its siblings duplicate the create-store, insert-metadata, load-additional-workspaces dance; one helper returning the populated store collapses them to a few lines each. RESOLVED DIFFERENTLY: the sibling this was written against, run_workspace_sql_query, was deleted in the lib.rs dead-code sweep (eb44) rather than kept and deduplicated — it had zero production callers. run_workspace_raw_query is now the only function doing this dance; extracting build_workspace_store for a single caller would be a premature abstraction, not a fix. no code change needed" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#requiresContext> <urn:context:cli> ;
